# Project Architecture

This project is a Cloudflare Worker REST API that validates and solves sudoku puzzles

Authoritative implementation layout:
- `src/index.ts`: HTTP routing and request/response shaping only
- `src/auth.ts`: bearer token auth only
- `src/sudoku.ts`: solver logic only (no HTTP concerns)
- `src/validate.ts`: validation analysis and reasons only
- `tests/*.test.ts`: unit/integration coverage

Rules:
- Keep routing concerns out of solver/validation modules.
- Keep solver internals out of `index.ts` handlers.
- Prefer pure functions and deterministic outputs.
- Keep TypeScript strict and avoid `any`.
- Preserve Cloudflare Worker compatibility (no Node-only runtime APIs in `src/*`).
